'''KoreKorea'''（{{lang-ko|'''꼬레꼬레아'''}}）一詞是表示[[南太平洋|南太平洋]]島國[[吉里巴斯|吉里巴斯]]為[[南韓|南韓]]漁[[船員|船員]]提供[[性交易|性交易]]的女子<ref>{{cite web |publisher=The Hankyoreh |date=9 July 2005 |url=http://legacy.www.hani.co.kr/section-001100000/2005/07/001100000200507090244001.html |title=The Shame in 'KoreKorea' |accessdate=2013-11-25 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202233922/http://legacy.www.hani.co.kr/section-001100000/2005/07/001100000200507090244001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。南韓漁民多利用[[金錢|金錢]]、[[衣物|衣物]]、魚貨等利誘吉里巴斯[[未成年|未成年]]女子從事非法性交易<ref name=Risky>{{cite web |title=Risky Business Kiribati: HIV prevention amongst women who board foreign fishing vessels to sell sex |publisher=International HIV Research Group, School of Public Health and Community Medicine, The University of New South Wales |url=http://www.fsm.ac.fj/files/Risky%20Bussiness%20Kiribati-%20HIV%20prevention%20amongst%20women%20who%20board.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030210044/http://www.fsm.ac.fj/files/Risky%20Bussiness%20Kiribati-%20HIV%20prevention%20amongst%20women%20who%20board.pdf |archivedate=2013-10-30 |accessdate=2013-11-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Commercial Sexual Exploitation of Children (CSEC) and Child Sexual Abuse (CSA) in the Pacific: A Regional Report |year=2006 |publisher=UNICEF, UNESCAP and ECPAT |url=http://www.unicef.org/eapro/Pacific_CSEC_report.pdf |5= |ref=CITEREFUNICEF2006 |accessdate=2013-11-25 |archive-date=2018-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180326141623/https://www.unicef.org/eapro/Pacific_CSEC_report.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其女子年齡多位於14至18歲，屬於未成年性交易，引發吉里巴斯政府嚴重關切以及當地民眾的不滿<ref>{{cite web |title=2012 Trafficking in Persons Report - Kiribati |publisher=United States Department of State / UNHCR |date=19 June 2012 |url=http://www.refworld.org/cgi-bin/texis/vtx/rwmain?page=country&category=&publisher=&type=&coi=KIR&rid=45b632e02&docid=4fe30cba48&skip=0 |accessdate=2013-11-25 |archive-date=2018-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180326064016/http://www.refworld.org/cgi-bin/texis/vtx/rwmain?page=country&category=&publisher=&type=&coi=KIR&rid=45b632e02&docid=4fe30cba48&skip=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Gender Issues in Tuna Fisheries Case Studies in Papua New Guinea, Fiji and Kiribati |publisher=The Pacific Islands Forum Fisheries Agency |url=http://www.ffa.int/system/files/%252Fhome/ffaadmin/%252Ffiles/ffa/Gender%20issues%20in%20P.I.%20tuna%20industries%20II%20.pdf |date=June 2008 |page=31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110220191528/http://www.ffa.int/system/files//home/ffaadmin//files/ffa/Gender%20issues%20in%20P.I.%20tuna%20industries%20II%20.pdf |archivedate=2011-02-20 |accessdate=2013-11-25 }}</ref>。

==南韓船員的增加==
位於[[赤道|赤道]]附近的[[南太平洋|南太平洋]][[島國|島國]]擁有世界第三大排他[[經濟海域|經濟海域]]。自1980年代起，許多[[南韓|南韓]][[遠洋漁船|遠洋漁船]]赴當地進行漁撈作業，每年約有數百名[[南韓|南韓]][[船員|船員]]在[[吉里巴斯|吉里巴斯]][[首都|首都]][[塔拉瓦環礁|塔拉瓦環礁]]上岸。

==KoreKorea的產生==
隨著[[塔拉瓦環礁|塔拉瓦環礁]]的[[南韓|南韓]][[船員|船員]]增加，[[性犯罪|性犯罪]]的問題開始層出不窮。南韓船員以金錢、衣物、食品等[[物資|物資]]利誘當地未成年青少女進行非法性交易，其多位於[[海岸|海岸]]防坡堤等漁船停靠處進行性交易<ref name=chosuned>[http://japanese.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2007/02/28/20070228000036.html "【社説】南太平洋キリバスの「醜い韓国人」"] {{Wayback|url=http://japanese.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2007/02/28/20070228000036.html |date=20070310071140 }}, [[朝鮮日報|朝鮮日報]], 2007/02/28.</ref>。

==KoreKorea的問題==
[[吉里巴斯|吉里巴斯]]最高[[民意代表|民意代表]]機構[[吉里巴斯國會|吉里巴斯國會]]將KoreKorea視為國家嚴重社會議題，在經過媒體報導KoreKorea的醜聞後，該會曾於2003年下令禁止[[南韓|南韓]][[漁船|漁船]]停靠吉里巴斯的任何[[港口|港口]]，以及不配發新的[[捕魚|捕魚]]執照予南韓籍漁船來解決問題。2007年[[吉里巴斯國家青少年委員會|吉里巴斯國家青少年委員會]]發表南韓漁船員仍於吉里巴斯境內與KoreKorea進行非法性交易<ref>{{ko icon}} [http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr/economy/2007/02/23/0301000000AKR20070223159900002.HTML {{Wayback|url=http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr/economy/2007/02/23/0301000000AKR20070223159900002.HTML |date=20150215200749 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr/economy/2007/02/23/0301000000AKR20070223159900002.HTML |date=20150215200749 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr/economy/2007/02/23/0301000000AKR20070223159900002.HTML |date=20150215200749 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr/economy/2007/02/23/0301000000AKR20070223159900002.HTML |date=20150215200749 }} "{{lang|ko|한국선원, 키리바시 아동성매매 지속 충격}} (韓国船員キリバス児童売買春が依然続き衝撃)"], [[韓國聯合通訊社|韓國聯合通訊社]], 2007/02/23.</ref><ref>{{en icon}} Kim Rahn, [http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/news_view.asp?newsIdx=3083017 "Sailors Blamed for Child Sex Trade"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/news_view.asp?newsIdx=3083017 |date=20070927191544 }}, [[韓国日報|韓国日報]]英語版, 2007-02-25.</ref>。另外，因為與南韓船員進行[[性交易|性交易]]而[[懷孕|懷孕]]的KoreKorea所生下的孩子亦成為社會問題。

另一方面，南韓籍漁船員因為性交易而為吉里巴斯帶來[[人類免疫缺陷病毒|人類免疫缺陷病毒]]HIV-AIDS。根據塔拉瓦綜合醫院的資料指出，有43名KoreKorea因與南韓船員進行性行為而染上[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]毒，其中26名患者更因此喪命<ref name=PM200611>{{en icon}} Ben Bohane, [http://www.pacificmagazine.net/issue/2006/11/01/fish-and-ships "Kiribati-Fish And Ships-Fishing Fleets Pose Social and Environmental Challenges"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pacificmagazine.net/issue/2006/11/01/fish-and-ships |date=20081007130735 }}, ''Pacific Magazine'', November 1, 2006.</ref>。

